import React from "react"
import { Container, Screen, Previous, Current, Button } from './Styled'

export default function Calculator() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Screen>
                <Previous>10 +</Previous>
                <Current>10</Current>
            </Screen>
           <Button gridSpan={2}>AC</Button>
           <Button></Button>
           <Button operation>รท</Button>
           <Button></Button>
           <Button></Button>
           <Button></Button>
           <Button operation></Button>
           <Button></Button>
           <Button></Button>
           <Button></Button>
           <Button operation></Button>
           <Button></Button>
           <Button></Button>
           <Button></Button>
           <Button operation></Button>
           <Button></Button>
           <Button></Button>
           <Button gridSpan={2}>=</Button>
        </Container>
    )

}
